    <item>
      <title>石油流量连续第四个月下滑，这次是因为利比亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/oil-flows-slump-for-fourth-straight-month-this-time-on-libya</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受利比亚政治争端引发供应中断影响，9 月份海运石油流量连续第四个月下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/oil-flows-slump-for-fourth-straight-month-this-time-on-libya</guid>
