    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚要求已经不服从的债券持有人接受 18% 的减记</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ethiopia-asks-already-defiant-bondholders-to-take-an-18-haircut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚提议其 10 亿美元债券持有人在债务重组中承担 18% 的损失，尽管它承认一群有影响力的投资者事先拒绝了这一提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ethiopia-asks-already-defiant-bondholders-to-take-an-18-haircut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:40:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着经济情绪好转，南非首席执行官们看到了“复苏的曙光”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/south-african-ceos-see-green-shoots-as-economic-mood-improves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非两家最大金融服务公司的首席执行官表示，自联合政府成立以来，人们对南非的情绪有所改善，但国家需要警惕自满情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/south-african-ceos-see-green-shoots-as-economic-mood-improves</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:40:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
