      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:37:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国铁路 140 亿欧元铁路部门出售案面临决定性投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/deutsche-bahn-s-14-billion-logistics-sale-faces-decisive-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国铁路股份公司计划以 143 亿欧元（158 亿美元）出售其物流部门，该交易将于周三面临决定性投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/deutsche-bahn-s-14-billion-logistics-sale-faces-decisive-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行十月降息势头似乎不可阻挡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ecb-momentum-for-an-october-rate-cut-is-looking-unstoppable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在三周前，欧洲央行官员还认为降息不太可能，但现在看来，当他们于 10 月 17 日再次确定借贷成本时，降息几乎已成定局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ecb-momentum-for-an-october-rate-cut-is-looking-unstoppable</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BBVA 在派发股息后向 Sabadell 收购报价注入现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/bbva-adds-cash-to-sabadell-takeover-bid-as-both-pay-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BBVA 调整了对 Banco Sabadell SA 的收购要约，包括增加一项新的现金部分，以补偿两家银行的股息支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/bbva-adds-cash-to-sabadell-takeover-bid-as-both-pay-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:19:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗袭击事件后避险购买减少，黄金回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/gold-holds-near-record-as-mideast-escalation-stokes-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列誓言对伊朗的导弹袭击进行报复后，市场等待中东冲突不断扩大的下一步行动，金价在周二飙升之后下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/gold-holds-near-record-as-mideast-escalation-stokes-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 23:02:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
